title: What this channel means to me | Mannymua
description:
Instageezy: Mannymua733 

I basically wanted to have a heart to heart with you guys about what I wanted this channel to be about and the message I wanted to convey. 

Growing up religious is amazing and I loved every second of my upbringing and its made me the man I am today, however its not all rainbows and unicorns. It was very tough for me and my family coming to the relization that I was gay. It has been 6 years since my outting, maybe ill make a coming out story video, and its been a long journey! Coming into my own and loving myself. 

I really want to convey a powerful message for other gay men, especially ones who are in the cosmetic industry, that it is okay to be you! Regardless of what people say or the hate you may get.

I STILL get hate on the daily, but I brush it off for the most part because I know who I am and no amount of hate will deffer me from doing what I love. And thats what I want you guys to get from this channel.

That everything will be okay, I promise. Just believe and trust in yourself.
